'''''Boesman na Lena''''' ni ikinamico ngufi yakorewe muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] ikozwe na  Athol Fugard,  Swartkops mudflats hamwe na  Port Elizabeth mur Cape town y'iburasirazuba, <ref>[http://www.encyclopedia.com/arts/educational-magazines/boesman-lena "Boesman & Lena"], Encyclopedia.com.</ref> yerekana ingaruka ya apartheid ku bantu bakeya,  hagaragaramo "umugabo n'umugore bagenda bava mu mujyi umwe bajya mu wundi.

== Amavu n'amavuko ==
Mubisanzwe hamwe nibindi bikorwa byinshi bya Fugard, ikinamico yibanda ku bantu batari abazungu kandi ikubiyemo ibintu byo kwigaragambya. ''Boesman na Lena'' batewe inkunga n'ibyabaye mu 1965 igihe Fugard yari atwaye mu umuhanda wo mu cyaro muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo. Yabonye umukecuru ugenda mu muhanda izuba ryamwishe, ku bilometero uvuye aho agana, maze amuha lift. Yaratsinzwe ararira ashimira. Yamubwiye ko umugabo we yari amaze gupfa kandi ko yari yagiye mu rindi sambu. iyo Fugard adahagarara, yari kurara kumuhanda.  (Byari akamenyero muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo ivangura rishingiye]] ku gitsina abahinzi birukana imiryango y'abakozi igihe umukozi yapfaga. ) Icyatangaje Fugard nuko umugore yari afite ububabare  ariko akaba ataratsinzwe. Ibi byamuteye kwandika ikinamico.
